## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The historical complexity of Chinese civilization means that multiple factors contribute to its longevity, and this report highlights only a few. Additionally, the sources used vary in academic rigor, with some being more anecdotal or opinion-based.

